headline: i2c Becomes First Issuer Processor Certified Globally to Enable Visa Click to Pay
summary: REDWOOD CITY, Calif., October 22, 2025--i2c Inc., a global financial technology innovator, today announced it is certified by Visa, a world leader in digital payments, to globally enable Click to Pay, the new global EMVCo standard in online checkout designed to improve security, authorization rates, and the overall eCommerce experience. With this certification, clients can enable Click to Pay across multiple regions through a single integration with i2c.
